For anyone wondering I figured that out /\

You need to make a var list and append numbers, then grab the total at the end or in between througout the loop
```{% set product_price_arr = [] %}
{% for item in repeater %}
  {% do product_price_arr.append(item.product_price) %}
{% endfor %}
{% set sum_up = product_price_arr|sum %}```
